# Styles: Non-Inline TailwindCSS
[globs]: ["**/*.{tsx,css}"]
- **NEVER use inline Tailwind** in .tsx files
- Use semantic classes from tv(); apply utilities in CSS via @apply
- Runtime customization via props.className (from Property Editor) is allowed
- **React Aria CSS naming**: Always use `react-aria-*` prefix (e.g., `react-aria-Button`)
- Check existing patterns in `src/builder/components/` before creating new CSS
- Reuse existing classes (e.g., `combobox-container`, `control-label`)
- Only add variant classes if needed (e.g., `react-aria-UnitComboBox`)
